Update,Soon,Easytobook,will,release,a,REST,API,Easytobook,provides,hotel,bookings,for,more,than,hotels,in,over,cities,The,Easytobook,API,provides,a,SOAP,based,API,to,facilitate,hotel,searching,and,booking,applications,Developers,can,retrieve,a,list,of,cities,get,hotels,for,a,particular,city,check,hotel,availability,look,for,cheap,hotel,rooms,get,other,room,information,retrieve,hotel,photos,and,other,hotel,information,as,well,as,book,the,hotel,on,behalf,of,their,users,Developers,can,also,retrieve,specific,booking,information,to,be,built,into,their,customer,service,applications,The,API,also,has,an,affiliate,program,to,pay,out,a,percentage,of,booking,fees,to,developers,Because,the,API,uses,SOAP,data,is,formatted,as,XML